{"tid":2348474,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一堆人完全搞不清楚狀況　北京他們要的是毀滅「黃絲」　使其不能再起　你是無法技術性回避的","createTime":"2020-12-31T16:59:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-31T23:55:28.000Z","uid":261647,"like":28,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"8052e9fb73f3034035e03900a251033d499e2630","tid":2348474,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T16:59:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cheng.lap.9/posts/10158807150007357\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcheng.lap.9%2Fposts%2F10158807150007357&d=h8K6dYNnEA4rSgnLcindhVEyhmTkDJ%2BTCVbHNRNdZc8%3D&h=a073aac2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cheng.lap.9/posts/10158807150007357</a><br />\n<br />\n如果你看的是東方人的書，你就會理解北京在做的是清算鏟除敵對勢力，跟清朝在消滅太平天國後做的事差不多。一堆人還在研究香港政府是否違法，是否違反法治，是否違反人道，或者基本法，或者雙重標準之類，完全搞不清楚狀況：他們要的是毀滅太平軍，即「黃絲」，使其不能再起，你是無法技術性回避的好嗎？<br />\n<br />\n對方擺明想整死你，還談法律法治制度人道道德之類是否有病。這是政治，不是在中學教通識教育。<br />\n<br />\n那些民主派天天講北京害怕人民的力量，既然你們懂這樣說，你們是否應理解東方人是怎樣對付自己害怕的東西的？消滅，因為害怕所以要斬草除根，有殺錯無放過，特別是你的經濟力量。<br />\n<br />\n約翰懷爾斯不會跟你說這套的，再讀幾千本討好國際政治哲學大師的書也沒用。人家談的是美國獨立後兩百年後的社會，而你在美國獨立前的社會。<br />\n<br />\n害怕你，對你來說並不是好消息好嗎。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nMythical Au:<br />\n讀過中史就略知一二，民變失敗最低消費係洗劫全城、流放為奴、徭役，屠城、滅族滅到全國改姓都好普遍。帝國首都唔會理城入面班人係咪「中立」，總之成個城成個省一齊罰。<br />\n<br />\nCheng Lap:<br />\n曾國荃屠南京，無分你是不是太平軍，香港班弱智就以為自己能置身事外<br />\n<br />\nMythical Au:<br />\n譚嗣同《北遊訪學記》：「頃來金陵，見滿地荒寒現象。本地人言：髮匪據城時，並未焚殺，百姓安堵如故。終以為彼叛匪也，故日盼官軍之至，不料官軍一破城，見人即殺，見屋即燒，子女玉帛，掃數悉入於湘軍，而金陵永窮矣。至今父老言之，猶深憤恨。」<br />\n<br />\nCheng Lap:<br />\n你看，人類真的不會進步"},{"pid":"581d075097132ce99d7eeafc257a60c0ed4396a0","tid":2348474,"uid":21545,"like":9,"dislike":9,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T17:01:42.000Z","msg":"我阿爸係男人<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n老衲都有用過鄭立<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1f7ad6b74887897a442721c81d4b6a0c6c7a85a","tid":2348474,"uid":69221,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T17:02:24.000Z","msg":"LM樓主被熱狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9b48d08ac9e2d38e5f247f4e73aa4138f373cac","tid":2348474,"uid":62180,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T17:02:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"890a51f04d060b1150f30bec02189b2e7d8bd57d","tid":2348474,"uid":357031,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T17:30:15.000Z","msg":"牠們要毀滅的是「香港人」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1b209b91792e03d1c0d4b111d7ac44d5db0df4c","tid":2348474,"uid":272580,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"581d075097132ce99d7eeafc257a60c0ed4396a0","tid":2348474,"uid":21545,"like":9,"dislike":9,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T17:01:42.000Z","msg":"我阿爸係男人<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n老衲都有用過鄭立<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T23:14:26.000Z","msg":"因人廢言就係你呢啲"},{"pid":"17df0ea40aa02b1bb08f4a9bc4147841d2d60c5c","tid":2348474,"uid":24024,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T23:18:19.000Z","msg":"事實"},{"pid":"66000423648f000ba281cae3f065e665d165ead0","tid":2348474,"uid":226296,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"581d075097132ce99d7eeafc257a60c0ed4396a0","tid":2348474,"uid":21545,"like":9,"dislike":9,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T17:01:42.000Z","msg":"我阿爸係男人<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n老衲都有用過鄭立<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"